  <entry>
    <title>GitHub、Gitee添加SSH认证</title>
    <url>/2022/03/10/GitHub%E3%80%81Gitee%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0SSH%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1）删除旧ssh文件"><a href="#1）删除旧ssh文件" class="headerlink" title="1）删除旧ssh文件"></a>1）删除旧ssh文件</h2><p>​        在c:&#x2F;用户&#x2F;用户名 下有一个.ssh文件夹，删除里面的旧文件，如果没有.ssh文件夹，新建一个</p>
<h2 id="2）生成ssh-key"><a href="#2）生成ssh-key" class="headerlink" title="2）生成ssh-key"></a>2）生成ssh-key</h2><ul>
<li><p>打开终端，执行下面指令（可以用git bash）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// github ---- SSH-key</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;aaa@xx.com&quot; -f ~/.ssh/github_id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">// gitlab ---- SSH-key</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;bbb@xx.com&quot; -f ~/.ssh/gitlab_id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">// gitee ---- SSH-key</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;ccc@xx.com&quot; -f ~/.ssh/gitee_id_rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="3）配置config文件"><a href="#3）配置config文件" class="headerlink" title="3）配置config文件"></a>3）配置config文件</h2><ul>
<li><p>cd ~&#x2F;.ssh</p>
</li>
<li><p>touch ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;config</p>
</li>
<li><p>在config文件添加如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="params">#</span> github</span><br><span class="line">Host github.com</span><br><span class="line">HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">PreferredAuthentications publickey</span><br><span class="line">IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github<span class="built_in">_</span>id<span class="built_in">_</span>rsa</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">#</span> gitee</span><br><span class="line">Host gitee.com</span><br><span class="line">HostName gitee.com</span><br><span class="line">PreferredAuthentications publickey</span><br><span class="line">IdentityFile ~/.ssh/gitee<span class="built_in">_</span>id<span class="built_in">_</span>rsa</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="4）上传key"><a href="#4）上传key" class="headerlink" title="4）上传key"></a>4）上传key</h2><p>&#x2F;&#x2F; GitHub<br>复制”github_id_rsa.pub”文件内容，添加至GitHub<br>&#x2F;&#x2F; Gitee<br>复制”gitee_id_rsa.pub”文件内容，添加至Gitee</p>
<h2 id="5）验证ssh"><a href="#5）验证ssh" class="headerlink" title="5）验证ssh"></a>5）验证ssh</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// GitHub</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">// Gitee</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@gitee.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><p>接着输入“yes”</p>
</li>
<li><p>若看到如下内容，则验证通过</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// GitHub</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Hi xxxx! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.&quot;</span><br><span class="line">// Gitee</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Hi xxxx! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but Gitee does not provide shell access.&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>若看到如下内容，则验证未通过</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// GitHub</span><br><span class="line">&quot;git@github.com: Permission denied (publickey).&quot;</span><br><span class="line">// Gitee</span><br><span class="line">&quot;git@gitee.com: Permission denied (publickey).&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>未通过，解决方案，输入如下指令</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 由于上诉通过&quot;ssh-keygen -t rsa -C&quot;生成的key是指定路径的，故此处需要手动执行如下指令：</span><br><span class="line">ssh-agent -s</span><br><span class="line">// GitHub</span><br><span class="line">ssh-add ~/.ssh/github_id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">// Gitee</span><br><span class="line">ssh-add ~/.ssh/gitee_id_rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
